   Hensleigh T 1988 pp 266-269 [LIG, TEXT, FER, DRA, TEMP, RAIN, LIMITS,
   USE]
   Troup R 1921 pp 485 [TEXT, USE, LIG, KTMP]
   Verheij E 1991 pp 256-257 [USE, LIG, DRA, TEXT]

